---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Singupuram Vamsi Krishna — philosopher, IIT Kharagpur & IIM Calcutta alumnus.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>
      I'm Singupuram Vamsi Krishna — a thinker drawn to questions of existence, consciousness,
      and how they quietly shape the choices we make every day.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most of my thinking circles back to one question: how does a deeper understanding of
      consciousness help us progress toward the realization of our own self? My ideas are grounded
      in non-duality, and I draw heavily from the works of Adi Shankara and Vivekananda.
    </p>

    <p>
      I'm also interested in game theory and mathematical frameworks as lenses on economics and
      business, and in how technology can genuinely serve human progress. Somewhere across
      philosophy, mathematics, and technology, I'm working toward a unified theory of progress.
    </p>

    <p>
      I graduated from IIT Kharagpur in Mechanical Engineering in 2021, then pursued an MBA at
      IIM Calcutta (2022–2024), graduating with Institute Rank 24 and the Institute Prize for
      finishing in the top 5% of my batch. I spent about ten months in investment banking before
      stepping back to do what I should have been doing all along — practicing yoga, reading deeply,
      and thinking.
    </p>

    <hr />

    <section class="contact">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:svkrishna.iitkgp@gmail.com">svkrishna.iitkgp@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a></li>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/themavisk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">github.com/themavisk</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }
  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }
  .contact h2 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  li {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  li a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
